;; How to use:
;; 0. Configure the keyboard shortcuts (see below)
;; 1. Run the command **Joyride: Run User Script**
;; 2. In your JS file, select code and evaluate with `ctrl+enter`
;;    Clear results decorations with `ctrl+escape`
;;
